Package: ERGMeta
Type: Package
Title: Meta-Analysis for Exponential Random Graph Models
Description: Tools to estimate Exponential Random Graph Models (ERGMs) across
    multiple networks, extract coefficient estimates and standard errors, and
    fit Bayesian meta-analytic models over ERGM parameters. Methodological
    background is discussed in Tolochko and Boomgaarden (2024)
    <doi:10.1016/j.socnet.2023.05.003>.
